  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study objective is to evaluate the change in mitochondrial uncoupling protein 2 (UCP2)
      mRNA expression as function of thyroid activity (TSH, T3 and Free T4).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Blood will be drown before thyroidectomy, 2 weeks after the operation and 3-4 month after the
      operation.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
